    "deployed": false,
    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces the CFB's already-open campaign-finance data (candidates, committees, contributions, expenditures, public matching-funds payments, disclosure statements) \u2014 most of which already answers live from the undocumented Follow the Money Web API (nyccfb.info/FTMSearchWebAPI) \u2014 and adds file_disclosure, the net-new write workflow locked today inside the C-SMART disclosure application.",
